<sect1 id="dir_a8f8c4b70d3587fcf7159bd2d30de216_1autotoc_md88">
<title>helios::engine::builder</title><para>Fluent builder pattern implementation for constructing game entities in the helios engine.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_a8f8c4b70d3587fcf7159bd2d30de216_1autotoc_md89">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides a declarative, composable API for creating <computeroutput>GameObject</computeroutput> instances with their associated components. The builder pattern enables clean, readable entity construction while abstracting the complexity of component dependencies and initialization order.</para>
</sect1>
